T02TD1546E:192b-1: shr'i badzra yo gi n'i mantra tatt'a //
T02TD1546E:192b-2: artha nir de sha sla aa dhi shath'a na n'a ma //
T02TD1546E:192b-4: dpal rdo rje rnal 'byor ma'i sngags kyi de kho na nyid kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i rim pa zhes bya ba //
T02TD1546E:192b-5: dpal rdo rje rnal 'byor ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1546E:192b-6: sngags gzugs rgyal ba'i dbang phyug ma //
T02TD1546E:192b-7: shin du 'jigs shing mchog ster byed //
T02TD1546E:192b-8: thig le phra mor nyer gnas pa //
T02TD1546E:192b-9: phyag 'tshal rdo rje phag mo dpal //
T02TD1546E:192b-10: yi ge re'i de kho na nyid //
T02TD1546E:192b-11: 'phral du yang dag yid ches byed //
T02TD1546E:192b-12: bgegs rnams thams cad rlag par byed //
T02TD1546E:192b-13: gsang sngags don ni bshad bar bya //
T02TD1546E:192b-14: bu yi yi ge'i mdun du blta //
T02TD1546E:192b-15: phyag 'tshal yi ge rab gsal ba //
T02TD1546E:192b-16: chos kyis lam de bshad par bya //
T02TD1546E:192b-17: rba rlabs med cing dri ma med //
T02TD1546E:192b-18: nyi ma lta bu'i rnam pa can //
T02TD1546E:192b-19: chos kun rab tu mi gnas pa //
T02TD1546E:192b-20: dngos dang dngos med rnam par spangs //
T02TD1546E:192b-21: blo dang ldan pas rtag tu bsgom //
T02TD1546E:192b-22: chos kyi sku ni thob 'gyur ba //
T02TD1546E:192b-23: blo ldan skye ba 'di yis ni //
T02TD1546E:192b-24: de la goms pa tsam gyis ni //
T02TD1546E:192b-26: rig byed dang po g-yon du bsam //
T02TD1546E:192b-27: longs sku spyod lam legs pa yin //
T02TD1546E:192b-29: shin tu legs pa'i 'od gsal ba //
T02TD1546E:192b-31: ji ltar brag ca 'dra ba yis //
T02TD1546E:192b-32: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:192b-33: rang rig bde ba'i mchog gyur ba //
T02TD1546E:192b-34: g-yas pa ye shes rgya mtsho ste //
T02TD1546E:192b-35: sprul ba'i lam ni dri ma med //
T02TD1546E:192b-36: sgyu ma lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD1546E:192b-37: chu zla 'dra bar bsam par bya //
T02TD1546E:192b-38: sbrul ba'i sku ni yang dag thob //
T02TD1546E:192b-39: me long gzugs brnyan 'dra ba bzhin //
T02TD1546E:192b-40: lhan cig skyes rnams rgyu mthun pas //
T02TD1546E:192b-41: bla na med pa'i go 'phang thob //
T02TD1546E:192b-42: aom yig gsum dang yang dag spyor //
T02TD1546E:192b-43: thig le yang dag bsdus pa gcig //
T02TD1546E:192b-44: de shes rab tu mi gnas pa //
T02TD1546E:192b-45: chos dbyings bdag nyid nges pa yin //
T02TD1546E:192b-46: yid ni der song sngags pa ni //
T02TD1546E:192b-48: bla na med pa'i lam spyad de //
T02TD1546E:192b-49: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis gsungs //
T02TD1546E:192b-50: sa yig ri bong can gzugs gnas //
T02TD1546E:192b-51: thig le lhan skyes mi 'jigs pa //
T02TD1546E:192b-52: de ni srog gis rnam par shes //
T02TD1546E:192b-53: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag gis //
T02TD1546E:192b-54: mdzod spu chen po'i sgo ru ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-2: dngos sgrub ma lus thob don du //
T02TD1546E:193a-3: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'gro //
T02TD1546E:193a-4: ba yig ra dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD1546E:193a-5: tshangs pa'i bu ga'i rnal 'byor byed //
T02TD1546E:193a-6: legs pa'i 'od zer rnam pa lnga //
T02TD1546E:193a-7: sna tshogs rdo rje rnam dag 'gro //
T02TD1546E:193a-8: dza yig nang du yang dag bsam //
T02TD1546E:193a-9: ji ltar me shel ji bzhin ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-10: gzhan gyis grong du 'jug par nus //
T02TD1546E:193a-12: bu yig chu bur rnam pa 'dra //
T02TD1546E:193a-13: dag pa'i shel dang mtshungs pa ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-14: 'gro drug rgyu ni bsreg byas nas //
T02TD1546E:193a-15: mngon shes drug gi go 'phang thob //
T02TD1546E:193a-16: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' nyid //
T02TD1546E:193a-17: yun mi ring bar nges par thob //
T02TD1546E:193a-18: aom yig la gnas rnam par lta //
T02TD1546E:193a-20: dha yig gnyis med ngo bo ste //
T02TD1546E:193a-21: stong nyid snying rje'i bdag nyid can //
T02TD1546E:193a-22: glog dang byi ru yang dag 'dra //
T02TD1546E:193a-23: aa yig nang du sang gnas pas //
T02TD1546E:193a-24: nyin mtshan dag par bsgom pa las //
T02TD1546E:193a-25: 'phral du yid ches byed pa ste //
T02TD1546E:193a-26: mkhas pas bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-27: ci phyir ngo mtshar gsal mi 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193a-29: bde ba'i gzhi ni zla 'od can //
T02TD1546E:193a-30: go yig nang du rnam bsgoms pas //
T02TD1546E:193a-31: mkha' la spyod pa nus par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193a-32: gi yig rgya skyegs med tog mtshungs //
T02TD1546E:193a-34: ra yig nang du yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:193a-35: 'od kyi phung por rnam par bsgoms //
T02TD1546E:193a-36: bsgoms pas bde ba yang dag skye //
T02TD1546E:193a-38: phyi nas thub dbang go 'phang ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-39: byang chub mchog ni thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193a-40: ni yi yi ge nad sel ba //
T02TD1546E:193a-41: aindra n'i la ltar nus pa //
T02TD1546E:193a-42: de yig snying por yang dag 'byung //
T02TD1546E:193a-43: ston ka'i zla ba lta bur bsgom //
T02TD1546E:193a-44: yang dag bla ma'i man ngag ste //
T02TD1546E:193a-45: lha yi mig gis blta bar bya //
T02TD1546E:193a-46: spyan ltar po ni thob 'gyur te //
T02TD1546E:193a-47: de tshe sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193a-48: yi yig mkha' 'dra'i ye shes ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-50: rnal 'byor chen pos lta bar byed //
T02TD1546E:193a-51: ma yig nang du yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:193a-52: mnyam pa nyid kyi yid kyis ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-53: the tshom med par bsam par bya //
T02TD1546E:193a-54: rgas dang 'chi ba rnam par spangs //
T02TD1546E:193a-55: bla na med pa rab tu 'thob //
T02TD1546E:193a-56: ba yig thig le zlum po ni //
T02TD1546E:193a-57: mdzes pa'i skar ma slad chen 'dra //
T02TD1546E:193b-0: ka yig bzhi la yang dag @193b gnas //
T02TD1546E:193b-1: bsgom bya rang bzhin g-yo med pa //
T02TD1546E:193b-3: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub byed //
T02TD1546E:193b-4: dngos dang dngos med rnam par grol //
T02TD1546E:193b-5: lus can gyis ni mngon sum byed //
T02TD1546E:193b-6: me yi sa bon gzi brjid ldan //
T02TD1546E:193b-8: ao yig dbus su gzhag par bya //
T02TD1546E:193b-9: legs pa'i blo yis rtag tu bsams //
T02TD1546E:193b-10: nam mkha' bsregs pa tsam gyis ni //
T02TD1546E:193b-11: dngos grub ri yi bdud rtsi 'dzag //
T02TD1546E:193b-12: de yis yang dag byugs tsam gyis //
T02TD1546E:193b-13: byang chub gser ni thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193b-14: wa yig kha dog sna tshogs pa //
T02TD1546E:193b-15: gzhan yang yid bzhin nor bu ltar //
T02TD1546E:193b-16: tri yig dbus su yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:193b-17: mar khu'i me bzhin 'bar ba yis //
T02TD1546E:193b-18: nyon mongs ma lus bsreg byas na //
T02TD1546E:193b-19: khams dang dbang po la sogs kyang //
T02TD1546E:193b-20: legs zhu he ru ka yi mchog / bla na med pa myur du thob //
T02TD1546E:193b-21: nna yig ra dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD1546E:193b-22: yi ge gsum ni che bar 'bar //
T02TD1546E:193b-23: ko yi yi ge'i phug tu gzhag /
T02TD1546E:193b-24: blo dang ldan pas rang sems bsgom //
T02TD1546E:193b-25: 'byung ba mchog tu dga' ba ste //
T02TD1546E:193b-26: srid dang mya ngan 'das ngo ni //
T02TD1546E:193b-27: rab 'jug bral bas dga' ba ste //
T02TD1546E:193b-28: bya ngan 'das pa'i chos ni bsam //
T02TD1546E:193b-29: lhan cig skyes dga' mi g-yo ba //
T02TD1546E:193b-30: lhan cig sbyor bas nang du gnas //
T02TD1546E:193b-31: bsgom pa brtan par 'gyur pa yin //
T02TD1546E:193b-32: bla na med pa'i go 'phang thob //
T02TD1546E:193b-33: autpala sngon po lta bu yi //
T02TD1546E:193b-34: ni yig sngon po'i thig le ni //
T02TD1546E:193b-35: ka yig sgo yi dbus gnas par //
T02TD1546E:193b-36: me shel lta bur bsgom par bya //
T02TD1546E:193b-37: de yi dbus su song ba'i sems //
T02TD1546E:193b-38: bde ba chen pos yongs su gang //
T02TD1546E:193b-39: sgyu ma lta bu'i ting 'dzin gnas //
T02TD1546E:193b-41: yi ge nyi ma'i gzugs dang 'dra //
T02TD1546E:193b-42: de yi dbus su bde mdzad ma //
T02TD1546E:193b-43: la yig phug tu yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:193b-44: dri ma bral ba rtag tu bsgom //
T02TD1546E:193b-45: sems ni de ru song ba la //
T02TD1546E:193b-46: rang rig pa ni thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193b-47: rang rig rnal 'byor pa de yis //
T02TD1546E:193b-49: ba yig glog 'gyu'i rnam pa ni //
T02TD1546E:193b-50: snang ba sgra yi rjes chags skyes //
T02TD1546E:193b-51: ka yig dbus su yang dag blta //
T02TD1546E:193b-52: dus mtshan nyid ni log par byed //
T02TD1546E:193b-53: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gnas //
T02TD1546E:193b-54: n'a da'i mtha' ni ye shes ltar //
T02TD1546E:193b-55: der gnas sems ni yang dag 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:193b-56: phyag rgya chen po mngon par thob //
T02TD1546E:194a-2: dzra yig ji ltar 'bar ba ni //
T02TD1546E:194a-3: hi yig la gnas bzhi brjod che //
T02TD1546E:194a-4: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin can //
T02TD1546E:194a-5: rtogs pa med pa'i sbyin sreg gis //
T02TD1546E:194a-6: yul dang dbang po'i tshogs pa rnams / de yis me lha mnyes gyur nas //
T02TD1546E:194a-7: dgyes pas dngos grub ster bar byed //
T02TD1546E:194a-8: bee yig thig le'i rang bzhin ni //
T02TD1546E:194a-10: sre yig rtse mor blta bar bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-11: lhan cig skyes dga' mi g-yo bar //
T02TD1546E:194a-12: srid dang mya ngan bral bas ni //
T02TD1546E:194a-13: dri ma med pa'i 'bras bu thob //
T02TD1546E:194a-14: rtag tu goms pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD1546E:194a-15: skye ba 'di la dngos grub thob //
T02TD1546E:194a-18: gri yig bshad pa'i lam la gnas //
T02TD1546E:194a-19: 'od ldan thig le bsgom par bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-20: rnam par snang mdzad gzi brjid che //
T02TD1546E:194a-21: bsgrub bya thams cad bsam par bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-22: yun mi ring ba'i dus kyis ni //
T02TD1546E:194a-23: sangs rgyas chen po thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:194a-24: zla ba chu shel lta bu'i 'dra //
T02TD1546E:194a-25: rtsa yig mdzes par bsam par bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-26: so yig nang du yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:194a-27: rnal 'byor pa yis rtag tu bsgom //
T02TD1546E:194a-29: bzhi ba'i sku yi mchog gi mchog / rtag tu goms pa'i rnal 'byor gyi //
T02TD1546E:194a-31: ni yig dri ma med pa nyid //
T02TD1546E:194a-32: sprin bral nam mkha' lta bu yi //
T02TD1546E:194a-33: su yig yi ge'i nang gnas pa //
T02TD1546E:194a-34: nyin dang mtshan du bsgom par bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-35: dngos dang dngos med rnam grol ba //
T02TD1546E:194a-36: chog tu zhi ba'i cha dang bral //
T02TD1546E:194a-37: bsam gtan tsam gyis yang dag thob //
T02TD1546E:194a-38: mtha' spyod gnas su khrid par byed ;
T02TD1546E:194a-39: / yi yig rang bzhin med pa yi //
T02TD1546E:194a-40: stong nyid phra la rdul med pa //
T02TD1546E:194a-41: na yig gnas pa'i yang dag lha //
T02TD1546E:194a-42: 'od ldan rang bzhin dri ma med //
T02TD1546E:194a-43: de yi dbus su sems gzhag pa //
T02TD1546E:194a-44: dngos dang dngos med rnam par spangs //
T02TD1546E:194a-45: srid las grol ba blta bar bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-46: sangs rgyas nyid ni grags pa bstan //
T02TD1546E:194a-47: phat yig ser po thig le ni //
T02TD1546E:194a-48: rtse mi rnams la mar lta bu //
T02TD1546E:194a-49: sa yig nang du gzhag par bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-50: 'dod ldan drang zhing bsam par bya //
T02TD1546E:194a-51: nyon mongs khams ni yang dag bsregs //
T02TD1546E:194a-52: phung po khams ni zad par 'gro //
T02TD1546E:194a-54: skye ba dang ni 'chi ba spangs //
T02TD1546E:194b-1: yid kyi sprul pas mdzes pa'o //
T02TD1546E:194b-2: ma yig gzhon pa rnam par blta //
T02TD1546E:194b-3: yid la sing ba yod snyam byed //
T02TD1546E:194b-4: sgyur ma la ta bur yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:194b-5: dri za yi ni grang khyer ltar //
T02TD1546E:194b-6: sems kyi 'jug pa tsam gyis ni //
T02TD1546E:194b-7: de la go 'phang bla na med //
T02TD1546E:194b-8: ha yig phal ma yang dag gnas //
T02TD1546E:194b-10: ku yi dbus su yang dag blta //
T02TD1546E:194b-11: thig le rang bzhin dri ma med //
T02TD1546E:194b-12: bsgom pa bstan par 'gyur pa yis //
T02TD1546E:194b-14: yun mi ring ba'i dus kyis ni //
T02TD1546E:194b-15: go 'phang bla na med pa thob //
T02TD1546E:194b-16: hri bri'i yi ge'i dbus su ni //
T02TD1546E:194b-17: yid du 'ong ba'i sangs rgyas gnas //
T02TD1546E:194b-18: drag po gsum dang ldan pa la //
T02TD1546E:194b-19: de'i dbus gsal bar bsgom pa'o //
T02TD1546E:194b-20: g-yas na mar me nyi ma'i cha //
T02TD1546E:194b-21: drod dang snying rje sprul ba'o //
T02TD1546E:194b-22: nyin mo rab gnas ye shes grags //
T02TD1546E:194b-23: dus dang thabs kyis kun rdzob po //
T02TD1546E:194b-24: lho ru rgyu bab 'du ba ste //
T02TD1546E:194b-25: rtsa nas khrag ni 'bar bar byed //
T02TD1546E:194b-27: lus ni mya ngan 'das bsgom bya //
T02TD1546E:194b-28: g-yon gyi h'um gi yi ge dkar //
T02TD1546E:194b-29: rnam shes rmi lam zla ba nyid //
T02TD1546E:194b-30: byang du 'gro ba shes rab brjod //
T02TD1546E:194b-31: stong nyid mtshan mo de bzhin du //
T02TD1546E:194b-32: 'jug pa'i lam ni longs spyod rdzogs //
T02TD1546E:194b-33: chu ni 'bab par byed pa'i rtsa //
T02TD1546E:194b-34: tshang pa mya ngan 'das par grags //
T02TD1546E:194b-35: nye ba'i nyon mongs zad byed pa //
T02TD1546E:194b-36: mdun du sngon po drag po ste //
T02TD1546E:194b-37: snying la a'a yig mi g-yo ba //
T02TD1546E:194b-38: gnyis med ye shes zhes brjod pa //
T02TD1546E:194b-39: dmigs med dri ma med pa'o //
T02TD1546E:194b-40: chu shing me tog yang dag 'dra //
T02TD1546E:194b-41: til gyi mi mar bzhin du 'bar //
T02TD1546E:194b-42: nyon mongs kun ni zad par byed //
T02TD1546E:194b-43: der song sems ni mya ngan 'das //
T02TD1546E:194b-44: chos kyi lam zhes ye shes ni //
T02TD1546E:194b-45: yang dag ye shes mchog gi mchog / yun mi ring bar thob 'gyur te //
T02TD1546E:194b-46: rdo rje sems dang mnyam par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:194b-47: dku gsung rang bzhin zhes brjod pa //
T02TD1546E:194b-48: dbus su thog lo gzhi med pa //
T02TD1546E:194b-49: lhan cig skyes pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
T02TD1546E:194b-50: sems can kun la rnam par gnas //
T02TD1546E:194b-51: de ltar bsgoms pa'i rnal 'byor bas //
T02TD1546E:194b-52: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:194b-53: rab tu mi gnas 'bras thob pas //
T02TD1546E:194b-54: bla na med pa bzhi ru 'gro //
T02TD1546E:194b-55: a'a li k'a li 'gog pa las //
T02TD1546E:194b-56: ri bo de ni nges par sbyar //
T02TD1546E:194b-57: rang bzhin 'od gsal mchog gi mchog //
T02TD1546E:195a-2: phra mor byas pa'i sems nyid ni //
T02TD1546E:195a-3: mi g-yo nyid du 'gro ba yi //
T02TD1546E:195a-4: de yi longs spyod bsams pa yi //
T02TD1546E:195a-5: lhun gyis grub pa rtag pa nyid //
T02TD1546E:195a-6: de ltar gus pas rgyun mi 'chad //
T02TD1546E:195a-7: bsgom pa yun ring rnam par bsam //
T02TD1546E:195a-8: yun ring bsgoms pa'i yid kyis ni ;
T02TD1546E:195a-9: / bde ba chen po thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1546E:195a-10: de ni do ha ko shar gsungs //
T02TD1546E:195a-11: sa bon gcig la sdong po gnyis //
T02TD1546E:195a-12: rgyu mtshan des na 'bras bu gcig //
T02TD1546E:195a-13: dbyer med de ni mngon byas pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-14: de ni srid 'das rnam par grol //
T02TD1546E:195a-15: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud las gsungs //
T02TD1546E:195a-16: thig pa sna tshogs thabs tshul gyis //
T02TD1546E:195a-17: 'gro ba'i don la rtog pa po //
T02TD1546E:195a-18: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung ba //
T02TD1546E:195a-19: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
T02TD1546E:195a-20: nyon mongs khams rnams dag pa'i bdag //
T02TD1546E:195a-21: las ki khams rnams zad byed pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-22: chu bo'i rgya mtsho kun las rgal //
T02TD1546E:195a-23: sbyor ba'i dgod pa las byung pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-24: nyon mongs nye ba kun nyon mongs //
T02TD1546E:195a-25: bag chags bcas pas gtan spangs pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-26: snying rje chen po shes rab thabs //
T02TD1546E:195a-27: don yod 'gro ba'i don byed pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-28: 'du shes gsum gyis don spangs pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-29: rnam shes don ni 'gag par byed //
T02TD1546E:195a-30: sems can kun yid yul dang ldan //
T02TD1546E:195a-31: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs rig pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-32: sems can kun gyi yid la gnas //
T02TD1546E:195a-33: de ltar de shes rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1546E:195a-34: gang zhig blo ldan rtag tu slob //
T02TD1546E:195a-36: bsod nams dman pa'i mi yis kyang //
T02TD1546E:195a-37: the tshom med par de yis 'grub //
T02TD1546E:195a-38: gus pas sgrub pa po yis ni //
T02TD1546E:195a-39: gus bcas ston pa mchod bya zhing //
T02TD1546E:195a-40: las rnams kun la gus par bya //
T02TD1546E:195a-41: ro gcig gis brjod rnam par rmongs pa'i sems kyis bsgom pa yang dag gsal don du //
T02TD1546E:195a-42: rtsa dang khams ni mnyam nyid mkha' 'gro mar ldan gnas la sogs pa'i sa rnams dang //
T02TD1546E:195a-43: de nyid re re'i dbye ba byas las dpal ldan rdo rje lha mo'i thugs //
T02TD1546E:195a-44: bde ba ro gcig gang la gsang ba sum cu rtsa gnyis de nyid dri ma med pa ni //
T02TD1546E:195a-45: sngags don nges bstan byas pa la //
T02TD1546E:195a-46: bdag gi dge ba gang bsgrubs pa //
T02TD1546E:195a-47: dpal ldan phyag rgya chen po'i go 'phang ni //
T02TD1546E:195b-0: des ni 'gro rnams myur du 'grub gyur cig / mchog tu za ba pa dpal dan rdo rje rnal 'byor ma'i sngags kyi de kho na nyid nges @195b par bstan pa //
T02TD1546E:195b-1: slob dpon aindra bh'a tis mdzad pa rdzogs rung bar 'dug nas rdo rje rnal 'byor ma bsgom pa pa brtson phab pa'o//
